Usage: create_inst_space_group [-help] <groupName> -inst <inst list> {[{[ -spacing_y <value>] [-spacing_x <value>]} [-checking_box {all|cross_only}]] | [-spacing_radial <value>]}

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
<groupName>                        # space group name (string, required)
-checking_box {all cross_only}     # checking all area or intersection area
                                   # from -spacing_x & -spacing_y (enum, optional)
-inst <inst list>                  # instance list (string, required)
-spacing_radial <value>            # radial spacing (in micron)
                                   # (float, optional)
-spacing_x <value>                 # x spacing (in micron) (float, optional)
-spacing_y <value>                 # y spacing (in micron) (float, optional)